source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage projects

Usage: mf project [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  new      Create a project
  list     List projects
  archive  Archive a project (not yet implemented)
  status   Show project status
  lint     Lint a project
  index    Index projects

Options:
      --root <PATH>      
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
